{"tid":218268,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔開心, 我老母係老師，個老女人校長成日針對佢...有咩計","createTime":"2017-04-26T11:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T07:17:57.000Z","uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9efba5c4c6c41b07ca91f3ff062d75296986d262","tid":218268,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"雖然就唔係鬧我，但成日見老母返到黎好唔開心，今日仲喊埋...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話校長成日針對佢，話佢呢樣做得唔好，個樣做得唔好，但我老母絕對係實幹派，可能唔係滿分，但絕對唔會差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n個校長成日搞針對某個老師，就係想逼佢走....例如比勁多野個老師做，開會既時候在所有人面前鬧佢之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最賤係用親近既人，明明有條友，死老野黎，去咩學校都唔會請，佢因為識所以請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要學校入面，d擦鞋仔長期狐假虎威，借校長之名周圍寸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老母想唔做，但仲有好多年，d公積金好多唔想無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但見到佢咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跪求大能之士，有無d咩方法可以緩攻/自保/玩返轉莊閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909a689e20bc21ef3db002d0876480c9989109d6","tid":218268,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"世上無難事....<br />\n只要肯屈服<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗下份人工，無咩熬唔到既"},{"pid":"32a54049cf477556d9e5f4bb7b5149154f1cd3dc","tid":218268,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"好多學校都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我以前讀個間中學都係，<br />\n求自保好嗱，佢地班人應該好有手段。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29629de439ec87b02990dd6b895e466ea000a167","tid":218268,"uid":74259,"